data.description: This property boasts beautiful LAKE VIEWS of George Lake, creating a serene and picturesque backdrop from the back of the house. Inside is a 4BR/2BA ranch-style home. The front door enters into the eat-in kitchen. New tile backsplash 2022. You just can't take your eyes off the lake from the living room big picture window. Down the hall are 3 bedrooms, and a 3/4 bath with tons of storage in the extra large vanity and built-ins. Step in accessible shower recently installed. Off the kitchen is the convenient 1-car attached garage, and also the lower staircase to the basement. The lower level has a rec room on the back of the house, again with gorgeous lake views, and a walk out door to a large paver patio to sit and enjoy the tranquil water. The basement also has another bedroom and 3/4 bath. A kitchenette helps you entertain in the lower level with ease. Windows replaced in 2012. New concrete driveway and garage door 2021/2022. Kitchen appliances stay. Located on a quiet dead end road.
